---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-8">About Folio</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
        This is a non-profit project to provide blogging, portfolio, and resume hosting functionality. The cost to maintain is offset by members and we want to provide a low maintenance platform for like-minded folks to publish their work.
      </p>
      
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
        We accept contributions from any like-minded folks who are willing to cost share the maintenance. We have a board which governs the rules and regulations of this project.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Important Guidelines</h2>
      
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
        All the work published here should be your own and should not represent your employer's views. We want to maintain long-term archival of this content for 30+ years.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
      
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Our mission is to create a sustainable, community-driven platform where professionals and enthusiasts can share their knowledge, showcase their work, and build their online presence without the burden of high hosting costs or complex maintenance requirements.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Join Our Community</h2>
      
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
        If you're interested in contributing to this platform or becoming a member, please reach out to our board. Together, we can maintain this valuable resource for years to come.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>